snippet.title: Nindo: Shinobi War - Clips #8
snippet.description:
Collection of clips from a few days of recent testing. 

Apologies for the ridiculous length of the video. I wanted to show some new things, give a general idea of how character progression as a whole is coming along and also keep in a decent amount of multiplayer gameplay to help show the state of the game. 
I've added timestamps to this video to help with the viewing experience considering the length. 

Games Discord: https://discord.gg/nindo
Help support the game if you want to, purely optional: 
https://www.patreon.com/Akyet

0:00 Intro
2:07 Clothing Store
2:58 Lost Cat Retrieval
5:15 Taijutsu Training
6:31 Passives/Trait Unlocks
7:19 Dropping Money
7:36 Grinding Missions for Renown
9:46 Scroll Retrieval Mission
18:31 Multiplayer Combat 1
28:52 Second Nature Release
29:43 Melee Weapon Store
30:00 Joining Sand Village
34:45 Steal Village Scroll Mission
39:41 Traveling to Uchiha Hideout 
44:49 Taijutsu Trainer
45:11 Multiplayer Combat 2
59:15 Outro
